        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1265471058" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1869804892083275662">I was so excited to get to read an early copy of this book. Hubert Crouch has outdone himself with this second book. From the very beginning it has you hooked, and with the plot twists and amazing characters, you won&apos;t want to put it down. <br/></span>
  <span id="freeText1869804892083275662" style="display:none">I was so excited to get to read an early copy of this book. Hubert Crouch has outdone himself with this second book. From the very beginning it has you hooked, and with the plot twists and amazing characters, you won't want to put it down. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="1869804892083275662" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


